flowRoot.flowPara: Propose a 20 minute talk or panel for one of the open slots today: add a sticky note and with the title and your name to the list below. You can submit as many proposals as you like! The proposals with the most votes will be selected at 14:40 and added to the schedule.
Keeping chickens - an adventure in poultry
You can vote once on each proposal, but on as many proposals as you want. To vote, add a tick below the proposal.
